    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi everyone! I\u2019m looking to pass along my trusty ride to a new owner! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion for me and is still in really solid shape. It drives great and has plenty of life left for all your road trips. I\u2019ve truly enjoyed my time with this car, and I think you will too! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
